title: 90 day Deposit Rate in Venezuela
description: 90 day Deposit Rate in Venezuela was at 36 percent on Thursday November 10. Deposit Interest Rate in Venezuela averaged 18.23 percent from 1997 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 108 percent in March of 2021 and a record low of 0 percent in October of 2021. The Deposit Interest Rate is the average rate paid by commercial banks to individuals or corporations on deposits. This page includes a chart with historical data for Deposit Interest Rate in Venezuela.
author: Banco Central de Venezuela
